      About this item

      • Easily Organize Your Collection - Forget sifting through piles of cards, struggling to find the one you need! Keep your card collection organized with our pack of 2 card trays that make sorting & organizing your collection a breeze.
      • 15 Card Compartments - Our Ding Defend trading cards & sports card organizer has 15 compartments. Each section can hold up to 100 cards, so you'll never run out of space for your growing collection.
      • Compatible with Various Cards - From raw cards to sleeved or toploader cards, our Storage Standard card tray can accommodate all your sports cards. Includes 15 trading card dividers!
      • Stackable to Maximize Space - Store your cards in our booster pack dispenser! Our card game organizer can be stacked atop one another, so you can watch your collection grow vertically & easily access each compartment.
      • A Must-Have for Card Collectors - Into collecting or trading cards? Whether you're a dedicated hobbyist, a seasoned card breaker, or a savvy reseller, our playing card display is what you need! Click 'Add to Cart' now to organize your cards!

      Set the Bar High with Simple Yet Reliable Solutions from Ding Defend by Storage Standard

      Tired of sifting through stacks of cards? Say goodbye to chaotic card collections and hello to effortless organization of your card collection with our Card Sorting Tray!

      Our card sorting tray is designed to simplify the tedious task of organizing trading cards. With the innovative design of our card pack dispenser that features built-in compartments, you can easily sort and categorize your collection. No more struggling to find the card you need among messy piles.

      Designed to house your extensive personal card collection or your inventory, our card sorting tray has 15 compartments. Each compartment can hold up to 100 cards, giving you plenty of room for expanding your collection. With our game card organizer, you can store large portions of your collection in one convenient location without worrying about running out of room.

      Say goodbye to complications and hello to simple, straightforward solutions from Ding Defend by Storage Standard!

      Game-Changing Organizer for Collectible Cards

      Generous Storage Capacity

      Designed with 15 compartments, each capable of holding up to 100 cards, you'll never have to worry about running out of room again with our card trays for playing cards! It also comes with 15 card dividers, so you can sort and categorize your cards any way you want!

      Accommodates Various Cards

      Whether you prefer to keep your cards in their raw state, protect them with sleeves, or showcase them in top loaders, our card sorting tray is compatible with all formats. Designed to organize all your card collection, our card sorter for playing cards measures 17 inches x 13 inches x 2 inches.

      Durable for Years of Use

      Crafted from premium plastic, our card sorter tray boasts a durable construction that's built to withstand the rigors of regular use. A more cost-effective alternative to flimsy organizers, our playing card display stand won't break or warp easily—ensuring it will last for years.

      Card-Friendly Angled Design

      The angled design of our card sorting tray ensures that your cards are not only neatly organized, but also prominently displayed. This angled layout makes it easy to view and access your cards, enhancing the overall presentation of your collection—be it in your gaming room or your store!

      Stackable to Maximize Limited Space

      Be it on your desk or a display shelf in your gaming room, our space-saving sorting tray allows you to make the most of your available space. Its stackable design lets you maximize storage space by allowing trays to be stacked vertically. Each tray remains easily accessible, so you can quickly retrieve your cards.

      Ideal for Card Breakers & Collectors

      Whether you're a sports card dealer or a gaming card trader, our trading card organizer will keep your inventory and prized collection neatly organized. Easily categorize and display your cards on our trading card sorting tray and eliminate the tedious task of constantly having to sort and arrange your collection!

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      Amazon Customer
      5 out of 5 stars
      Fantastic sorting tray!
      I collect Pokemon/Yugioh/One Piece cards. Bought this because I figured it’d be easier to use a sorting tray to organize my out-of-control amount of TCG cards rather than making random piles everywhere and covering entire tables with a mess of cards. Fantastic deal and purchase! This came in a two pack, along with around 12 plastic dividers, and it really gets the job done and makes sorting cards SO much easier! The size is just right: each tray comes with 30 slots, with each slot potentially being able to hold around 30-70 cards before it becomes full (just an estimate, can’t remember the exact number). The trays are stackable, so it makes transporting them a breeze. I like to bring them to my local game shop on my days off and spend a couple hours finding/sorting through single cards that they have that I need :)
